Creates a pseudo-element as the first child of the selected element. Requires `content` property.

Example:
```css
.icon::before {
  content: '';
  display: inline-block;
  width: 16px;
  height: 16px;
}
```

Defines the keyframes for an animation sequence.

Syntax:
```css
@keyframes name {
  from { /* start state */ }
  to { /* end state */ }
}
```
Or with percentage stops:
```css
@keyframes name {
  0% { opacity: 0; }
  50% { opacity: 0.5; }
  100% { opacity: 1; }
}
```

