documentation.value:
Applies styles based on the size of a containing element (not the viewport).

Requires `container-type` on the parent:
```css
.parent { container-type: inline-size; }
@container (min-width: 400px) { .child { ... } }
```
Named containers: `container-name: sidebar;` + `@container sidebar (...) { }`

